        "sections": [
          {
            "name": "Hippo Sweat",
            "sources": [
              {
                "link": {
                  "alt": "Monster Core 2 pg. 191",
                  "aonid": 276,
                  "game-obj": "Sources",
                  "name": "Monster Core 2 pg. 191",
                  "type": "link"
                },
                "name": "Monster Core 2",
                "page": 191,
                "type": "source"
              }
            ],
            "text": "A hippopotamus\u2019s sweat is an unusual reddish color that can lend them an even more frightening appearance, evoking the visage of a blood-coated monster. This sweat helps to protect the hippopotamus from becoming overheated, but it also bolsters their resistance to all manner of diseases.",
            "type": "section"
          }
        ],
        "sources": [
          {
            "link": {
              "alt": "Monster Core 2 pg. 191",
              "aonid": 276,
              "game-obj": "Sources",
              "name": "Monster Core 2 pg. 191",
              "type": "link"
            },
            "name": "Monster Core 2",
            "page": 191,
            "type": "source"
          }
        ],
        "text": "Hippopotamuses, or hippos for short, are semiaquatic animals that spend most of their time in rivers and lakes, but can thrive on land.",
        "type": "monster_family"
      },
